data.name: Zurrein Resort
data.description:
Nestled in the crystal-clear waters of the Indian Ocean, this five-star resort in the Maldives offers an unforgettable escape to paradise. With its powder-soft white sand beaches, vibrant coral reefs, and turquoise lagoons, this resort promises guests an idyllic getaway.

The resort features overwater villas and beachfront bungalows, each designed with modern luxury in mind. The overwater villas provide direct access to the ocean, offering breathtaking views of the sunset from private decks. Guests can relax in their spacious, beautifully furnished rooms, complete with open-air bathrooms, outdoor rain showers, and plunge pools for the ultimate indulgence.

data.name: Unique HangingTree House
data.description:
A Unique HangingTree House located in the woods in Dalarna, Sweden. The tree house can be found hanging between two huge trees and is a wonderful place to truly feel away from it all. The rental can sleep two guests as there is a double bed inside, although one additional youngster can sleep on the twin bed that folds out from the couch if necessary. The rental is kept toasty warm, despite the setting up in the trees, thanks to the fireplace inside that burns real wood and there is also underfloor heating installed.

Guests will also have access to the communal living space on the property during their vacation. Here, there are full bathroom facilities and also a kitchen space where guests can prepare meals. Breakfast and dinner provisions are provided and there is plenty of dining space available both inside and out.

Guests will have no trouble making themselves at home during a stay in this property. Linens and towels are provided and guests can also take advantage of the maid service. To keep guests cozy, there is both a heater and underfloor heating installed.

Outside, guests can enjoy grilling on the BBQ while soaking in views of the forest from the terrace. There are also various communal spaces for guests to make the most of, including a small swimming pool, a play area, and a trampoline for younger guests to enjoy.
